"},{"content":"Add coconut milk and water. Place Varoma with cauliflower into position, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>10 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside and stir cauliflower."},{"content":"Add sweet potato, pumpkin, salt and cashews to mixing bowl. Place Varoma back into position, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>10-15 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>, or until cauliflower is cooked. Remove Varoma and set aside."},{"content":"Add broccolini to mixing bowl and cook <b>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>."},{"content":"Add snow peas and spinach, then stir to combine with aid of spatula. Cook <b>1 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>. Season to taste."},{"content":"Serve curry with cauliflower rice and garnish with coriander, natural yoghurt and extra toasted cashews just before serving."}],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}